{% block content %}
<p>
	lib<span class="algo">Firm</span> is a C-library that provides an intermediate representation, optimisations, and backends for compilers. Programs are represented in a graph based <a class="external text" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Static_single_assignment_form">SSA form</a>.
</p>
