<ul>
	<li><b><a href="Download" title="Download">Download lib<span class="algo">Firm</span></a></b></li>
	<li> <a class="external text" href="http://github.com/MatzeB/JFirm/">JFirm</a> - Java-Bindings (aimed at compiler construction courses)]</li>
	<li> Tools
		<ul>
			<li><a class="external text" href="http://www.info.uni-karlsruhe.de/software/ycomp">yComp</a> - <i>visualization for program graphs</i></li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li> Frontends
		<ul>
			<li> <a class="external text" href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/cparser/">CParser</a> - C-Frontend</li>
			<li> <a class="external text" href="http://github.com/MatzeB/bytecode2firm">bytecode2firm</a> - Javabytecode frontend</li>
			<li> <a class="external text" href="http://github.com/MatzeB/fluffy">Fluffy Language</a></li>
			<li> <a class="external text" href="http://pp.info.uni-karlsruhe.de/git/firm-bf">brainfuck</a></li>
			<li><a href="Edgfe" title="Edgfe">C-Frontend (based on edison design group code)</a></li>
		</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

